name: LocationOptions
shortdesc: Options for specifying location relative to the reference object or within the containing object.

property.name: BEFORE
property.shortdesc: Places the object before the reference object.

property.name: AFTER
property.shortdesc: Places the object after the reference object.

property.name: AT_END
property.shortdesc: Places the object at the end of the containing object.

property.name: AT_BEGINNING
property.shortdesc: Places the object at the beginning of the containing object.
